      <div class="right">
        <p>Over the last several years, we have watched our innerspring mattress company, Saatva, grow from a mid-sized regional luxury mattress company to one of the largest online-only mattress companies in America, as more and more customers (like us) want a great product for a great price without the hassle. It’s a simple idea that has really caught on.</p>
        <p>We combine the best known luxury and eco-friendly materials and technologies in a mattress, we make it in America, and we sell it online so that customers don’t have to pay outrageous mark-up costs to get a decent nights’ sleep.</p>
        <p>The Loom & Leaf mattress has been a natural extension of our success. We wanted to extend our product line so that customers looking for a memory foam mattress could have the benefit of a better product and better buying experience. Utilizing the infrastructure we established with Saatva, we now have 11 factories throughout America fabricating our L&L mattresses, and over 32 fulfillment centers that deliver our mattresses coast to coast. The results of our model have been fantastic, and it shows in our customer reviews.</p>
        <p>We never forget that our company and our successes are built on individual consumer satisfaction and recommendations. It is this attitude that has helped us become the best reviewed mattress brand on Google in 2013-2015, and we will continue to serve our new and repeat customers each day going forward.</p>
