            <p>We are not only committed to giving customers a better nights’ sleep and a better buying experience, we are equally passionate about our planet and our communities. For us, it’s not enough to be good at what you do. The real proof of character is in giving back to those in need. In the last year we have donated hundreds of mattresses and partnered with over 10 organizations.</p>
